# AgToosa Revert Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-revert` or any rollback work, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Revert.md` precisely.

## Key constraints

- Always identify the exact phase or commit to revert to before touching any files.
- Create a git stash or backup branch before reverting — never lose uncommitted work.
- After revert, confirm the test suite passes at the target state.
- Update Linear and `Docs/Master-Plan.md` to reflect the rolled-back state.
